currentDoc:
Is Listening to a Book Just as Good as Reading It?

Do you listen to audiobooks? What are the benefits, in your opinion, of listening instead of reading? Are there advantages to reading that cannot be gained by listening? Which method do you prefer? Why?

---

In my opinion,

currentSuggestions.original: I do enjoy listening to audiobooks.
currentSuggestions.trimmed: I do enjoy listening to audiobooks.

currentSuggestions.original: Reading takes a lot of concentration focus and time.
currentSuggestions.trimmed: Reading takes a lot of concentration focus and time.

currentSuggestions.original: Odd as it seems, I will sometimes cook while listening to an audiobook.
currentSuggestions.trimmed: Odd as it seems, I will sometimes cook while listening to an audiobook.

currentSuggestions.original: It allows you to enjoy a book without getting a headache from reading.
currentSuggestions.trimmed: It allows you to enjoy a book without getting a headache from reading.

currentSuggestions.original: As a mother of six, I do not have time to read as much as I would like.
currentSuggestions.trimmed: As a mother of six, I do not have time to read as much as I would like.

ops.insert: It allows you to enjoy a book without getting a headache from reading.

currentSuggestions.original: I haven't personally ever listened to an audiobook while lying in bed, however.
currentSuggestions.trimmed: I haven't personally ever listened to an audiobook while lying in bed, however.

currentSuggestions.original: However, there are also some disadvantages to listening.
currentSuggestions.trimmed: However, there are also some disadvantages to listening.

currentSuggestions.original: It also allows you more time to hear the story especially when driving.
currentSuggestions.trimmed: It also allows you more time to hear the story especially when driving.

currentSuggestions.original: Also, if you are an auditory learner, this can really help you to make sense of the story.

currentSuggestions.original: Also, audiobooks can open the door to stories and authors that you never would have tried before.
